4:00 PM Registration & Welcome. Install Software.
5:00 PM Start of session - Modern ML Slides
5:30 PM Introduction to ML Slides
6:00 PM MLCC
9:00 PM Closing

Please review the CoC here : https://www.meetup.com/GDG-Cloud-RTP/about/

events.name: Weekly Study Session
events.description:
Will be meeting online via hangouts. As usual, I will share my screen as I work through a qwiklab. You can follow along or simply watch and comment.

We finished the IoT Core series of labs which focused on IoT registry and device, the training data and analyst device simulator, pub/sub. We also did labs for IoT which used DataPrep, DataFlow, FireBase, Kafka, BigQuery, Storage, Deployment Manager and Compute Engine.

I am open to any lab the group wants to work through, but I suggest we do the "Exploring APIs" quest. Its a series of 8 labs that all use the API explorer capability to exercise Cloud Storage, Clusters, Compute Engine, App Engine, Cloud SQL, Cloud Natural Language, etc.

Will be meeting online via hangouts. As usual, I will share my screen as I work through a qwiklab. You can follow along or simply watch and comment.

We finished the IoT Core series of labs which focused on IoT registry and device, the training data and analyst device simulator, pub/sub. We also did labs for IoT which used DataPrep, DataFlow, FireBase, Kafka, BigQuery, Storage, Deployment Manager and Compute Engine.

I am open to any lab the group wants to work through, but I suggest we do the "Exploring APIs" quest. Its a series of 8 labs that all use the API explorer capability to exercise Cloud Storage, Clusters, Compute Engine, App Engine, Cloud SQL, Cloud Natural Language, etc.
